                  "value": "Assist a celestial being on a divine quest to save the world."
                },
                {
                  "key": "Flaw",
                  "value": "Prejudice — A Profession: specifically toward soldiers"
                },
                {
                  "key": "Quirk",
                  "value": "They love telling this story: Bork Bumblebeard - A foolhardy protagonist of dwarvern tales, who's funny legendary mishaps serve as a reminder to dwarf children to pay attention to detail. Sometimes makes an appearance in other dwarvern tales as a friendly foil to a hero or just as comic relief. Sometimes older storytellers may insert one of Bork's antics into their story no matter how improbable as a way of playing a practical joke on the listener, similar to a Rickroll!"
                },
                {
                  "key": "Faith",
                  "value": "Cautious listener."
                },
                {
                  "key": "Keepsake",
                  "value": "A jar of a purple liquid, stolen from the rain gods. It belonged to a man formally known as a prince."
